# f_add
this is a function that adds two numbers
```javascript
let n1 = 1;
let n2 = 2;
let f_add=(n1,n2)=>{return n1+n2}
```
# f_sub
this is
`f_sub`, can be used to subtract numbers
```javascript
let f_sub(n1,n2)=>{return n1-n2}

```
## usage
```javascript
let b = 3 == f_add(1,2);
let b = 2 == f_sub(8,6);
```
